### Step 6 — Create the profile page `template/page-studs/profile/with-auth-trpc-tw.tsx`

This is a new file in a new subdirectory. The file naming follows the existing convention (`with-auth-trpc-tw.tsx`), the directory name mirrors how index pages are named (`profile/` as the route segment), and the component style mirrors `with-auth-trpc-tw.tsx` exactly: a named sub-component (`ProfileShowcase`) embedded in a full `NextPage` export (`Profile`), using `useSession` + Tailwind classes consistent with those already in the index stubs.

